2026-07-04 12:18:18,776 | crm | DEBUG | content='The final answer to the user\'s question "Business Analyst AI agent communication standards and quality standards" is:\n\nThe Business Analyst AI agent should follow these communication standards and quality standards:\n\n1. Clear and concise language\n2. Structured thinking and analysis\n3. Measurable and testable requirements\n4. Traceability and transparency\n5. Collaboration and stakeholder engagement\n6. Continuous learning and improvement\n7. Adherence to industry standards and best practices\n8. Use of agent communication protocols such as ACP and A2A\n9. Reliability and scalability\n10. Security and data protection\n\nThese standards and guidelines will ensure that the Business Analyst AI agent provides high-quality outputs and effectively communicates with stakeholders, while also maintaining the integrity and security of the data and systems involved.' additional_kwargs={'refusal': None} response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 159, 'prompt_tokens': 11415, 'total_tokens': 11574, 'completion_tokens_details': None, 'prompt_tokens_details': None, 'queue_time': 0.05312055, 'prompt_time': 0.751131649, 'completion_time': 0.483660336, 'total_time': 1.234791985}, 'model_provider': 'openai', 'model_name': 'llama-3.3-70b-versatile', 'system_fingerprint': 'fp_ba38bbab80', 'id': 'chatcmpl-202af5df-cad8-40e0-9164-85dea4f12100', 'service_tier': 'on_demand', 'finish_reason': 'stop', 'logprobs': None} id='lc_run--019f2ca2-9895-7851-a715-d41ce02836b4-0' tool_calls=[] invalid_tool_calls=[] usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 11415, 'output_tokens': 159, 'total_tokens': 11574, 'input_token_details': {}, 'output_token_details': {}}
